Privacy Policy
This privacy policy sets out how Vieyra Software uses and protects any information that you voluntarily provide to Vieyra Software when you use our apps or visit our website. Vieyra Software is committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected. Vieyra Software may change this policy from time to time by updating this page. You should check this page from time to time. This policy was updated and is effective as of 9 January 2022.
​
App Privacy
Downloading our apps does not require any registration of personal information with Vieyra Software. Vieyra Software does not collect any personally-identifying data on you or your use of any of our applications. However, Vieyra Software may make use of non-personally-identifying usage statistics (i.e., clicks, sensor mode usage, time in app, etc.). Vieyra Software does not access a user's sensor data of any type.
​
After installation, any physical data measurements recorded using the mobile device's sensors is stored in the internal memory of the mobile device, unless otherwise transmitted voluntarily by the user to a third party through the data export feature. Vieyra Software apps do
not
require Internet permissions.
App Permissions Explained
Each Vieyra Software app requires different levels of permissions depending upon the sensors capabilities of each app. At most, the following permissions are required for the following purposes:
Location: to determine precise location via the GPS (for the GPS mode)
Photos/Media/Files: to save and/or read recorded sensor data
Storage: to save and/or read recorded sensor data
Camera: to control the camera flash (for the Stroboscope mode)
Microphone: to collect audio information (for the Sound Meter, Tone Detector, Oscilloscope, and Spectrum Analyzer modes)
Other: to control the camera flash and to prevent the mobile device from entering sleep mode while collecting data
​
Website Privacy
Should we ask you to provide certain information by which you can be identified when using this website, then you can be assured that it will only be used in accordance with this privacy statement.
​
Data We Collect via Our Website
By voluntarily registering for our mailing list, responding to surveys, or otherwise contacting us through this website, we may collect the following information:
Name
E-mail Address
Other information relevant to surveys (demographic data, user feedback, etc.)
We do
not
monitor identifiable individual activity on our website via cookies.
​
What We Do with the Information We Gather via Our Website
Information that you voluntarily provide to Vieyra Software may be used to:
Contact you regarding feedback you provided to us
Keep you updated about new app features and usage ideas
(only if you voluntarily register for our newsletter)
Contact you for surveys to improve our website and our apps
(only if you voluntarily register for our newsletter)
​
Security
We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. In order to prevent unauthorized access or disclosure, we have put in place suitable physical, electronic, and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect via our website. Our website is hosted on Wix.com. Any data you submit through the newsletter registration feature is stored through Wix.com's data storage, which are protected on secure servers behind a firewall.
​
Controlling Your Personal Information
If you voluntarily registered for our newsletter and no longer prefer to be contacted by us, you may remove yourself from the list by clicking on the appropriate link at the bottom of any newsletter mailing.
​
We will not sell, distribute, or lease your personal information to third parties unless we have your permission or are required by law.
​
Links to Other Websites
Our website may contain links to enable you to visit other websites of interest easily. However, once you have used these links to leave our site, you should note that we do not have any control over that other website. Therefore, we cannot be responsible for the protection and privacy of any information which you provide while visit such sites and such sites are not governed by this privacy statement. You should exercise caution and look at the privacy statement applicable to the website in question.
​
Contact Us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using our website or our applications, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via e-mail at
support@vieyrasoftware.net
.
